information: Since 1939 our Company has been specialized in shelling almonds. We offer Marcona, Largueta, Valencias (spanish raw kernels) and we also manufacture Organic almond. We provide quality almond in bulk abroad. We can offer different sizes. Our company buy almonds direct from the farmer and after the process of shelling, we sell fresh and clean almonds, natural or blanched. Frutos Secos Gil S.L. is a family business of four generations. Visit our website to know more about us.
